## **************************************
## 
## Rotational motion
## Part 1
## By F. Wolfs,  WOLFS@NSRL.ROCHESTER.EDU,
## No unauthorized commercial use
## Imported Files:
## ${CAPA_Tools}Problem
## ${CAPA_GraphicsDirectory}Gtype21/prob12a.eps
## Values needing defined:
## prob_val (number, e.g. /LET prob_val=1)
## prob_try (number, e.g. /LET prob_try=5)
## 
